Contributions to this project are entirely welcome. A few pointers:

- This project is styled according to PEP8, with an extended line length of 120 characters instead of 80.
- The code uses type hinting where it makes sense.

When contributing, you should try to follow these conventions where it makes sense. If it doesn't make sense to do so,
or doing so is impractical, do something as close as possible without making your work or the code too much more
complicated.

Additionally, the project is licensed under the MIT license. Upon submission of any contribution to this project, You
grant a non-exclusive, perpetual, royalty-free, irrevocable, worldwide license to your contribution in whole under the
terms of the MIT license.